# Builder Repository Agents Guide

## Commit Message Format

- Subject: `<TICKET>: <short description>`
- Body: explain what was done and why
- Trailer: `Closes: <TICKET>`

## Package Placement Rules

- Default: add to CPU variant for the latest torch version
- Only add to CUDA/ROCm if the package depends on an accelerator stack
- Collection path: `collections/onboarding/<variant>/requirements/<package>.in`

## Linting

Run `make linter` before committing. Fix all errors.
